WEBVTT

00:00.007 --> 00:02.958
♪ ♪

00:10.134 --> 00:12.134
(dogs barking)

00:19.477 --> 00:21.860
♪ So follow me up 'cause this
... about to go down ♪

00:21.896 --> 00:22.861
(barking)

00:23.970 --> 00:26.387
♪ I'm doing 500,
I'm out of control now ♪

00:26.439 --> 00:28.055
♪ But there's nowhere to go now ♪

00:28.107 --> 00:29.724
♪ And there's no way to slow down ♪

00:29.726 --> 00:31.192
♪ If I knew what I knew in the past ♪

00:31.227 --> 00:33.227
- ♪ I would have been blacked
out on your ass ♪ - (dog snarling)

00:33.229 --> 00:35.029
♪ Come on, homie, what happened? ♪

00:35.063 --> 00:36.896
- ♪ You ... ain't breathing, you
gasping ♪ - (dog whimpering)

00:36.948 --> 00:39.032
♪ These ... ain't ready for action... ♪

00:39.067 --> 00:41.201
(rhythmic panting)

00:46.308 --> 00:48.208
♪ ♪

